<H3> <TI>   Intelligence, Counterintelligence Services Reunite </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Intelligence, Counterintelligence Services Reunite </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD1106123694 Moscow Radiostantsiya Ekho Moskvy in Russian 
1100 GMT 11 Jun 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD1106123694 </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow Radiostantsiya Ekho Moskvy </F>
<F P=105>  Russian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Russia's intelligence and counterintelligence 
services have reunited their work. This was confirmed by Sergey 
Stepashin today. However, he did not specify whether or not the 
Federal Counterintelligence Service and Yevgeniy Primakov's 
service [the Russian Foreign Intelligence Service of which 
Primakov is director] would be merging organizationally. 

</TEXT>

