<H3> <TI>   Crimea Presents Draft Treaty on Relations to Ukraine </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Crimea Presents Draft Treaty on Relations to Ukraine </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD1206125694 Moscow Radio Moscow World Service in English 
1200 GMT 12 Jun 94 </F>

