<H3> <TI>   Nuclear Power Plants Overfill Plan in May </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Nuclear Power Plants Overfill Plan in May </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD1306102194 Kiev UNIAR in Ukrainian 2300 GMT 12 Jun 94 </F>
<F P=103> LD1306102194 </F>
<F P=104>  Kiev UNIAR </F>
<F P=105>  Ukrainian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Summary] During May Ukraine's nuclear power stations 
produced 40.2 percent of the total quantity of electric power 
produced in the state. They produced 6.197 billion 
kilowatt-hours of electric power, or 104.8 percent of the plan. 

</TEXT>

