<F P=100> Turkmenistan </F>
<H3> <TI>   President Fines Officials for Negligence in Fires </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    President Fines Officials for Negligence in Fires </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   MK1006115394 Moscow SEGODNYA in Russian 10 Jun 94 p 5 </F>
<F P=103> MK1006115394 </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow SEGODNYA </F>
<F P=105>  Russian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

<F P=106> [Report by Mekhman Gafarly: "Niyazov Fines a Number of </F>
Republic's Leaders"] 
  [Text] Turkmenia [Turkmenistan] President Saparmurat 
Niyazov has by special edict imposed fines equivalent to three 
monthly salaries on the minister of internal affairs, the 
general prosecutor, the chairman of the National Security 
Committee, and the chief of the Republic's Border Guard Troops 
Directorate, as well as on the leaders of two rayons. All of 
them failed to take measures to prevent the fires in the 
Ashkhabadskiy and Gyaurskiy rayons, which have done considerable 
damage to the environment. The blaze started on 5 June and 
mainly engulfed the border zone. A separate decree has 
dismissed Nurmukhamed Ashirov, minister for the use and 
protection of the natural environment, and his deputy for the 
same reason. 
  The money will be transmitted to a special account to be 
opened by the Republic president's staff with the AKB 
"Turkmenistan" bank. In the future all fines for ecological 
crimes in the Republic will come to this account. 

</TEXT>

</DOC>

