BFN 

<F P=106> [By ITAR-TASS correspondent Aleksandr Romanov] </F>
  [Text] Beijing, 13 Jun -- During a visit to Moscow at the 
end of June by Qian Qichen, foreign minister and vice premier of 
the State Council of the PRC, an agreement between Russia and 
the PRC relating to the western section of the border between 
Russia and China will be initialled. This was agreed upon 
