BFN 

<F P=106> [Article by Vladimir Lepekhin, Mikhail Malyutin, Yuriy </F>
Sorokin, Grigoriy Vysokinskiy, Oleg Grigoryev, Vadim Malakhitov, 
Roman Pugachev, Ivan Sukhiy, Vladislav Sychev, Aleksandr 
Yusupovskiy: "Career Formula: The More Gently You Travel the 
Higher You Will Get: Influence Rating: May-June"] 
  [Text] 


