<H3> <TI>   Further on CPRF Call for Abolition of Presidency </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Further on CPRF Call for Abolition of Presidency </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   PM1306132194 Moscow SOVETSKAYA ROSSIYA in Russian 11 Jun 94 
p 1 </F>

